              <td>From &pound;2,000</td>
              <td>From &pound;3,000</td>
              <td class="total">From &pound;5,000</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Peak Season<br><span style="font-weight:400;font-size:12px;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;opacity:0.6;">May - Sep, Friday</span></td>
