      <div class="pricing-example">
        <p>For a Saturday wedding in peak season with 50 guests, a three-course dinner, four hours of unlimited drinks, and a flower package, the total is approximately &pound;8,350 + food and drink spend. That is one invoice, from one team, with no hidden extras.</p>
